summary: Unleash the beauty of grass by removing little rocks.
descriptionHtml:
[center][font=Lucida Sans Unicode][color=#efefef][size=3]
This mod simply removes little rocks coded as grass (when you type tg). Personally they were way too dense and had lego meshes.

As someone who loves to play with dense grass, rocks also gets denser which hurts my eyes. This mod unleashes the beauty of grass.[/size]
[/color][/font][/center]
author: ProtologolusX
